OL,3,C'We're not afraid': Gaza boy tells of
OL,4,Cmiracle survival after losing leg in
OL,5,Cblast
OL,7,FITV News Correspondent Lucy Watson met
OL,8,Fwith 12 year-old Abdallah Kehil whose
OL,9,Fleg was saved from amputation after a
OL,10,Frocket landed in front of his school.
OL,11,FHe continues with bravery and
OL,12,Fundiminished dreams to become a model.
OL,14,FThe war in Gaza has continued for
OL,15,Fnearly 11 months, and throughout that
OL,16,Ftime we have heard often about how it
OL,17,Fhas affected its children - who make
OL,18,Fup half of the territory's population.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
