OL,7,FThey are experiencing death and
OL,8,Fdestruction daily, and quite often,
OL,9,Fwitnessing the unimaginable.
OL,11,FRecently, I went to Egypt to report on
OL,12,Fdesperately ill Palestinians who,
OL,13,Funtil May, were allowed to leave Gaza
OL,14,Fto go to Egypt, and elsewhere, for
OL,15,Fmedical treatment.
OL,17,FOn our last day of filming in Cairo,
OL,18,Fwe were at the Nasser Institute
OL,19,FHospital talking to cancer patients
OL,20,Fand their doctors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
