OL,7,FThroughout the day, unbeknownst to us,
OL,8,Fwe were being watched. It was only
OL,9,Fwhen we started to pack up did the
OL,10,Fcurious 12 year old observer make
OL,11,Fhimself known.
OL,13,FHis name was Abdallah Kehil, and his
OL,14,Fresilience and bravery astounded us,
OL,15,Fbut not only us, the Egyptian
OL,16,Fpresident too.
OL,18,FAs he moved along the corridors of the
OL,19,Fhospital ward in his wheelchair,
OL,20,FAbdallah had an undeniable popularity
OL,21,Fand presence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
