OL,3,C'We're not afraid': Gaza boy tells of
OL,4,Cmiracle survival after losing leg in
OL,5,Cblast
OL,7,FThe other children adored him. He
OL,8,Fsmiled often and they followed him
OL,9,Flike the Pied Piper. But, Abdallah's
OL,10,Fsmile hid horrors no 12 year old
OL,11,Fshould ever see. He wanted to share
OL,12,Fhis own story, about a school day in
OL,13,FNovember.
OL,15,F"We were bombed, a rocket hit us in
OL,16,Ffront of our school," he said.
OL,18,F"We were sitting down and suddenly the
OL,19,Fmissile struck us. My leg was blown
OL,20,Foff. My friends' bodies were
OL,21,Fscattered."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
