OL,5,Cblast
OL,7,FAbdallah crawled along the ground away
OL,8,Ffrom the devastation. Medics found him
OL,9,Fand carried him to hospital where he
OL,10,Fhad to fight for his own life. He'd
OL,11,Flost every one of his friends.
OL,13,FOnce his condition stabilised, he made
OL,14,Fa video from his hospital bed in Gaza
OL,15,Fand put it online, asking the Egyptian
OL,16,Fpresident to save his leg.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
