OL,7,FJust days later, Abdallah and his mum
OL,8,Fwere rescued. Their evacuation was
OL,9,Fshown on Egyptian state television, as
OL,10,Fhe was moved from ambulance to
OL,11,Fambulance, hospital to hospital, until
OL,12,Fhe reached Cairo, and the Nasser
OL,13,FInstitute, where surgeons were waiting.
OL,15,FHe explained to me what they did to
OL,16,Ffix his leg.
OL,18,F"They took a muscle from my back and
OL,19,Fskin from my thigh, to repair my other
OL,20,Fleg. They put it back together as
OL,21,Fnew," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
