OL,7,FIn January, he was invited by
OL,8,FPresident Abdul Fattah El Sisi to a
OL,9,Fnational event at Cairo's New Capital
OL,10,FTheatre. It was there - on stage -
OL,11,Fthat Abdallah said to the audience, "I
OL,12,Fwish I could hug the President."
OL,14,FAt that point, El Sisi walked up on
OL,15,Fstage and hugged him. His survival
OL,16,Fdefies belief, but so too does his
OL,17,Fspirit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
